name: No Civility, Only Politics
Lore: 'It''s not rare to see a senator using the system to forward his own personal agenda. Much goes on behind closed doors that the Senate never sees.',
Text: 'USED: During your move phase, take one of your characters with politics at Galactic Senate into hand.LOST: If you have a Republican with politics in battle at a site, add one battle destiny; that character is power and politics = 0 until end of turn.',
